<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id8ed700f4-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6" identifier="/us/usc/t22/s287h"><num value="287h">§ 287h.</num><heading> Limitation on loan</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The total amount of money that may be loaned to the United Nations pursuant to the authorization contained in <ref href="/us/usc/t22/s287g">section 287g of this title</ref> shall not exceed the aggregate amount of loans made by other nations.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id8ed700f5-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6">(<ref href="/us/pl/87/731/s2">Pub. L. 87–731, § 2</ref>, <date date="1962-10-02">Oct. 2, 1962</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/76/695">76 Stat. 695</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="id8ed700f6-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="id8ed700f7-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I76" topic="codification" id="id8ed700f8-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Codification</heading>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Section was not enacted as part of <ref href="/us/act/1945-12-20/ch583">act Dec. 20, 1945, ch. 583</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/59/619">59 Stat. 619</ref>, known as the United Nations Participation Act of 1945, which comprises this subchapter.</p>
</note>
</notes>
</section>
